It becomes more interesting when we couple the Dirac field to an electromagnetic field through minimal coupling.
See Section 3.5.4 in Maggiore.

Regarding the polarization of $$\psi_\alpha(x)|0\rangle$$, we can apply the number operator $$N$$, which is similar to $$H$$
